id: BHV-mission-fsm
kind: behavior
name: Mission state machine
status: draft
conformance_level: structural
description: Event-driven finite state machine that drives the mission lifecycle. The VLM (planner) is called only at decision-point events, not on a timer. STUCK is the only recovery state; all paths terminate in RETURNING or LANDED.
satisfies: REQ-event-driven-planning, REQ-fsm-bounded
allocated_to: CMP-mission-computer
behavior_type: state_machine
states: PREFLIGHT, TAKEOFF, TRANSIT, ON_TASK, STUCK, RETURNING, LANDED
initial: PREFLIGHT
transition: PREFLIGHT -> TAKEOFF on arm_takeoff
transition: TAKEOFF -> TRANSIT on altitude_reached
transition: TRANSIT -> ON_TASK on waypoint_reached
transition: ON_TASK -> STUCK on no_progress [elapsed > 600 s]
transition: STUCK -> ON_TASK on waypoint_reached
transition: ON_TASK -> RETURNING on rtl_command
transition: ON_TASK -> RETURNING on map_boundary
transition: RETURNING -> LANDED on mode_changed [mode == LAND]
